snippet: Gracie Gold, the 2014 American champion, withdrew from the Grand Prix of Figure Skating finals in Barcelona, Spain.
abstract: American 2014 champion Gracie Gold withdraws from Grand Prix of Figure Skating finals with stress fracture in her left foot.
